full_text: I fear the day State Champs makes an accidental frat boy anthem
I swear to god State Champs is just the All Time Low of post 2010 pop punk
All I wanted to do was climb a tree today and instead I just have to fill my tank with money I don’t have again
I don’t think there’s a song that does more for me in the world that isn’t 40 Steps by the academy is
